April 25 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Friday. To inform us of other job changes, email to moves@thomsonreuters.com.

LOUIS DREYFUS COMMODITIES  The global trader said on Friday that Chief Executive Ciro Echesortu will step down and the group's finance head will take charge temporarily. [ID:nL6N0NH1VV]  BANK OF AMERICA CORP <BAC.N> The bank named Geoffrey Greener its new chief risk officer following Terry Laughlin's movement to a new role.